com.github.upthewaterspout.fates.core.threading.event

Class ThreadLocalEventListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.upthewaterspout.fates.core.threading.event.DelegatingExecutionEventListener
      • com.github.upthewaterspout.fates.core.threading.event.ThreadLocalEventListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExecutionEventListener

    public class ThreadLocalEventListener
extends DelegatingExecutionEventListener
    A decorator for a ExecutionEventListener that is only enabled for the current thread and any thread spawned by the current thread. This listener is used to make sure that only threads under test are controlled by the scheduler.
